					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Since the perverted law got amended, even a simple parody carries the risk of attracting animosity.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"只是单纯恶搞就算了──但是改成变态恶搞风格的话，的确就有可能会引起反感。",
